        <h2>
            朱镕基讲话实录 第四卷的书评 · · · · · ·
            <span class="pl">(<a href="reviews">全部 3 条</a>)</span>
        </h2>
    </header>


        


<div class="review-list">
  
  
      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="8003864">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8003864/" class="title-link">你以为转基因标识是为了生物安全？嘻嘻嘻</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8003864"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/caradillon/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/u1666456-18.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/caradillon/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">行动好比风拂柳</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-07-22"
      class="main-meta">2016-07-22 23:17:53</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8003864_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  2000年7月到2003年2月  最近看见个人写上海迪斯尼前世。除非有相反史料，否则就是阅读能力奇差，胡J8乱解释。  1. 网路工程  金关工程、金税工程原来是他推动的。  2. 西部大开发  主要是搞基础设施建设，而不是像79年做特区一样加工贸易、工业起家。产能过剩一直是朱的心头大...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/8003864/#comments">(3回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_8003864_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_8003864_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="5726933">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/5726933/" class="title-link">是真实录！</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-5726933"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/46980297/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/46980297/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">Jack Zhao</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2013-01-04"
      class="main-meta">2013-01-04 21:47:52</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_5726933_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                     这套书很不错，比其他的领导讲话集子更实在，推荐喜欢总理的人，关注政治、国家建设的读一读。    内容就不多说了，都是朱总理内部讲话，都是实话，干事情的话。读完最大的感觉是中国的总理真是不容易，特别是想有所作为的总理。

                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">0有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
